Description: 2016 American Stratocaster Deluxe Surf Green You are looking at a gorgeous Mint American Deluxe Fender Stratocaster! This is a true classic in a beautiful vintage color- Surf Green. The exposed areas on the front, back, and edges are like new- has never been played and is simply pristine. This is easily one of the best looking bodies Fender makes with a great contour heel for easier access to upper frets. This sweet baby is loaded with custom detailed work: Pearl Pickguard and Backplate, TV Jones Humbuckers, top of the line Deluxe Maple Neck. This is one of a kind! Neck: Maple neck with “soft V” profile, Bi-Flex™ truss rod and Micro-Tilt™ Compound-radius maple fingerboard (9.5”-14”) with 22 medium jumbo frets Designed for remarkable comfort and performance, with an attractively tinted satin finish and a “V”-shaped profile (the shape of the neck in cross section) ideal for players with large hands whose thumb extends well over the side of the fingerboard. Black abalone dot inlays. Pickups: TV Jones Classic Filter'Tron Pickup Set, ChromeFilter’Tron style pickup is a humbucker with a unique design with specific characteristics. Its dual-coil pickup design cancels the hum, and with a large 1/4″ alnico magnet (twice as large as a “standard” PAF magnet) and larger pole screws, the result is a higher inductance (more power – thicker tone). The Filter’Tron’s bobbins are positioned closer together and wound with less magnet wire for less loss of high end - With a Coil Tap! A TV Jones Filter’Tron pickup blends ALL of these traditional characteristics with select, specific top-quality USA-made components. This special recipe gives way to an un-parallelled tone, unique to TV Jones guitar pickups. This is an awesome looking and sounding Stratocaster - and its one of a kind! Don't let this one get away. Comes with a new locking fender case. Message me with questions...
